info.description:
DeviceIdentifier API Python library
===================================

Utils to manipulate and learn from assorted device identifier formats
via Reincubate‚Äôs `DeviceIdentifier
API <https://www.reincubate.com/deviceidentifier-api/>`__.

Technical documentation is available on `Reincubate‚Äôs
site <https://docs.reincubate.com/deviceidentifier/?utm_source=github&utm_medium=deviceidentifier-py&utm_campaign=deviceidentifier>`__.

Getting started
---------------

Try these:

.. code:: bash

   $ pip install deviceidentifier

Calls to the API through this client then become easy:

.. code:: python

   from deviceidentifier import api

   # Look up an Apple serial number
   api.lookup( api.TYPE_APPLE_SERIAL, 'C8QH6T96DPNG' )

   # Identify the type of an identifier
   api.identify_identifier( 'iPhone5,3' )

   # Triangulate a bunch of data from a collection of identifiers
   api.enhance_metadata(
       apple_identifier='iPhone5,3',
       apple_serial='C8QH6T96DPNG',
       gsma_imei='013554006297015',
       gsma_iccid='8965880812100011146'
   )

The API supports anonymous access, and provides limited, rate-limited
data when doing so. Tokens can be obtained by contacting
`Reincubate <mailto:enterprise@reincubate.com>`__, and either by setting
an environment variable:

.. code:: bash

   $ export RI_DEVID_TOKEN='api-authentication-token'

Or by passing the token value directly into the code:

.. code:: python

   from deviceidentifier import api

   # Look up an Apple serial number
   api.lookup( api.TYPE_APPLE_SERIAL, 'api-authenticaton-token', 'C8QH6T96DPNG' )

Need more functionality?
------------------------

Reincubate‚Äôs vision is to provide data access, extraction and recovery
technology for all app platforms - be they mobile, desktop, web,
appliance or in-vehicle.

The company was founded in 2008 and was first to market with both iOS
and iCloud data extraction technology. With over half a decade‚Äôs
experience helping law enforcement and security organisations access iOS
data, Reincubate has licensed software to government, child protection
and corporate clients around the world.

The company can help users with:

-  iCloud access and data recovery
-  Recovery of data deleted from SQLite databases
-  Bulk iOS data recovery
-  Forensic examination of iOS data
-  Passcode, password, keybag and keychain analysis
-  Custom iOS app data extraction
-  Advanced PList, TypedStream and Mbdb manipulation

Contact
`Reincubate <https://www.reincubate.com/?utm_source=github&utm_medium=deviceidentifier-py&utm_campaign=deviceidentifier>`__
